data.description: Cozy and comfortable this fully upgraded city cottage has plenty of space! A gorgeous Florida room opens up the home with more light and is perfect for early morning coffee. Your functioning layout provides space and relaxation. Enjoy a large yard that  is perfect for BBQs and entertainment. The oversized detached has shelving and makes great for a workshop. A must see!
